Women's polo model (polo-womens.glb)
====================================

This garment was supplied by the site owner (a photogrammetry scan, provided as a
~19.6 MB / 546k-vertex glTF). For the studio it was welded, decimated with the
meshoptimizer simplifier to ~74k vertices, had vertex normals recomputed, and was
re-centred and height-normalised, then re-exported as a compact binary glTF
(~3.5 MB). It carries no textures and is recoloured at runtime.

ACTION REQUIRED: confirm the original source and licence of this scan and record
it here (author, URL, and licence terms). If the scan is under a licence that
requires attribution (e.g. CC-BY) or restricts commercial use, that must be
honoured before the site goes live.
